Niger-2
Ogun-2
Akwa Ibom-1 156,496 confirmed
134,551 discharged
1,923 deaths “A breakdown of cases by state can be found via http://covid19.ncdc.gov.ng”. Meanwhile, the Nigeria’s allocation of the first batch of 3.92 million doses of the Oxford-AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine arrived the country yesterday amid jubilation from Nigerians.